input.command:
gh pr create --title "feat: #3 - Add audio and visual notifications when timer completes" --body "$(cat <<'EOF'
## Summary

Implements a comprehensive notification system to alert users when Pomodoro work sessions or break timers complete. This ensures users don't miss the end of a cycle and can smoothly transition between work and breaks.

## Implementation Plan

See [Implementation Plan](../blob/feature-issue-3-adw-7c425707-audio-visual-notifications/specs/issue-3-adw-7c425707-sdlc_planner-audio-visual-notifications.md)

Closes #3

**ADW ID:** 7c425707

## What Was Done

- [x] Created audio notification system with Web Audio API support
- [x] Implemented visual notification banner component with animations
- [x] Added browser notification support with permission handling
- [x] Built notification settings UI with localStorage persistence
- [x] Integrated notifications with timer completion events
- [x] Added E2E test suite for notification functionality
- [x] Implemented accessibility features (ARIA labels, screen reader support)
- [x] Added mobile-friendly audio support with unlock on first interaction

## Key Changes

**New Components:**
- `NotificationBanner.tsx` - Visual alert component with dismiss functionality and auto-dismiss
- `NotificationSettings.tsx` - Settings UI for toggling audio/browser notifications

**New Hooks:**
- `useNotifications.ts` - Central notification management with audio, visual, and browser notifications

**New Utilities:**
- `audio.ts` - Audio notification system using Web Audio API
- `types/notifications.ts` - TypeScript types for notification system

**Updated Files:**
- `PomodoroTimer.tsx` - Integrated notification settings UI
- `useTimer.ts` - Added notification triggers on timer completion
- `tailwind.config.js` - Added keyframe animations for notification banner

**Testing:**
- `.claude/commands/e2e/test_notifications.md` - Comprehensive E2E test suite
EOF
)" --base main
